4950x4950 px

Purple. It had to be done. What seems to be a beautiful, yet default colour to use amongst many NFT creators, I’d tried to avoid. I gave myself a challenge. 

Purple, I’ve discovered, often represents wealth, wisdom and spirituality. So we’ve got all bases covered with this piece. 

Even Joseph Albers and the colour theorists would be excited. Stare at the central negative space and it appears to be navy blue. 

It isn’t. It’s purple. Afterimage trickery.
